name: Vessels 168: Story Beat 08
description:
RAVAGE: THE RAID TO END ALL RAIDS!
4) We pick out a face in the crowd. A female pirate. This is SILVER. She looks calm, placid, in stark contrast to the sneering faces around her.
CAPTION: SILVER
RAVAGE (OFFSCREEN): WE WILL DESCEND ON THEIR PATHETIC TOURNAMENT AND UNLEASH THE FULL FUCKING FURY OF HELL UPON THEM! PLUNDER THEIR RICHES! KIDNAP THEIR WOMEN! KILL THEIR MANGY OFFSPRING! WE’RE GONNA TURN THEIR LITTLE FUCKING SPORTS DAY INTO A FUCKING BLOODBATH!
